Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 26, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
H.B. NO. 1643, H.D. 2, S.D. 2, RELATING TO PHARMACY.
C.D. 1 ACT 039
